# Favicon.ico Generation Instructions

This file should be replaced with an actual ICO file generated from the SVG favicon.

To generate the ICO file:

1. Use the SVG favicon.svg file in this directory
2. Convert it to ICO format using an online converter or image editing software
3. Ensure the ICO file includes multiple sizes: 16x16, 32x32, 48x48
4. Replace this file with the generated ICO

The SVG favicon is already properly configured in the layout.tsx file and will work in modern browsers. 